scripts.test: npm run test-ctags && npm run test-fuzzy-native && npm run test-pty

scripts.test-fuzzy-native: (cd fuzzy-native && npm install && npm run rebuild)
scripts.test-keytar: (cd keytar && npm install && npm run rebuild)
scripts.test-pty: (cd pty && npm install && npm run rebuild)
